block content
  p I don’t need to tell you that GIF’s have taken over. Each day!{' '}
    span.bold 7 billion
    |!{' '}are “served” to!{' '}
    span.bold 500 million
    |!{' '}people worldwide.
  p They all come from the same place: Giphy. Their!{' '}
    a(href="https://developers.giphy.com/") API
    |!{' '}powers pretty much every messaging app out there: Facebook, Instagram, Snap, Tik Tok, etc.
  p This has opened up quite a novel way for brands to get exposure. If you get your GIF (or sticker) on Giphy you get it everywhere. And you can then overlay the GIF with your logo, product or even a URL to increase brand awareness.
